snippet: Will it have a quantifiable effect in nurturing start-ups and creating jobs?
abstract: Will it have a quantifiable effect in nurturing start-ups and creating jobs?
lead_paragraph: It's been a year since business leaders gathered at the White House to kick off the Startup America Partnership, a national nonprofit initiative intended to spur the growth of new companies, with the end goal of creating jobs.

headline.main: After a Year, Startup America Has a Start
